{"tid":1993753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解讀侵玫瑰園講話：班農認為對支共可以採取\"對恐怖分子的報復行動\"","createTime":"2020-04-29T03:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T03:57:01.000Z","uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1cda92975c67b306b7923fc96757be33f5f0bd","tid":1993753,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"班農@WarRoomPandemic<br />\n解讀川普總統玫瑰園講話：#依法滅共，全面啓動！<br />\n<br />\n班農還提到可以採取&quot;對恐怖分子的報復行動&quot;，比如採用當年對沙特啓用的《制裁恐怖主義資助者法案(JASTA)》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1255259681037189122?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1255259681037189122%3Fs%3D20&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=282c89f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1255259681037189122%3Fs%3D20&h=b0ec3c9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1255259681037189122?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n川普總統玫瑰園講話：「我們有很多方式追責<br />\n我們正在進行嚴肅深入調查美國的索賠要比德國的1300億歐元多得多而且在方式上容易很多」<br />\n<br />\n此外，他還再次暗示中共可能蓄意放毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1255231695269265408?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1255231695269265408%3Fs%3D20&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=33406062\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1255231695269265408%3Fs%3D20&h=1bb2ff9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1255231695269265408?s=20</a>"}]}